snippet.title: Namco Museum Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the OG Evercade Handheld.
NOTE: This cart is NOT compatible with the Evercade VS. It only works with the OG Evercade and the Evercade EXP.

Games in this cart:
00:08 - Battle Cars (SNES)
03:37 - Dig Dug (Famicom)
06:40 - Galaxian (Famicom)
08:51 - Libble Rabble (Super Famicom)
14:22 - Mappy (Famicom)
19:23 - Mappy Kids (Famicom) [Official English Translation]
22:18 - Metal Marines (SNES)
32:00 - Pac-Man (Famicom)
35:30 - Quad Challenge (MegaDrive / Genesis)
40:20 - Star Luster (Famicom)
45:58 - Xevious (Famicom)
